Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:07.13,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:15.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:27.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.98,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The party headed to the Witches' Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:38.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,to break the curse that Vetto \Nhad placed on Asta's arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:41.03,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and they found Vanessa in a wretched state.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:42.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.54,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you think you are,\N but get your foot off of her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:52.75,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the brat \NVanessa was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.86,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,This foolish little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:01:00.58,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,told me she'd become my slave and \Nlive out the rest of her days here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.81,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for healing your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Vanessa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:11.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the party began their battle with \Nthe Queen of Witches, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.06,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,They were much faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:21.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,New enemies arrived at the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:23.08,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:29.58,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Spirit Magic: Salamander's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing how powerful the enemy was,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:36.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Queen of Witches healed Asta's arms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and let him protect the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! They're completely better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:51.35,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:58.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the Queen of Witches's healing \Nmagic, Asta's arms were better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:02.03,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His battle with Fana, who was\N filled with hatred, began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:06.29,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:10.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll just keep throwing \Nyour attacks right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.89,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Flames of Hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your \Nattacks right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:00.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:05.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your attacks right \Nback at you over and over and over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.99,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's built up a lot of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,since he couldn't use his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.95,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.29,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,This time we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.67,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.80,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.88,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Spirit Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.93,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander's Talon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:47.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.75,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Salamander,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:59.11,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,said to have the highest attack \Npower of the Four Great Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:04.05,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a spirit that matches \Nthe military power of an entire nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.81,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.31,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits are mana-based lifeforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.63,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's anti-magic sword can \Nslash apart mana itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.63,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:26.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was scary! But it's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:30.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're so lucky! I want a Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.36,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:35.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But that old guy, Vetto, was much \Nfaster and had better senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.37,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,...has a chance of winning this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:46.88,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Watching you makes \Nbeing scared seem silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Why are these flames so powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's like throwing water on burning rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:08.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm basically just wasting mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Asta and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.63,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hurt us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.68,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.54,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for our counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Let's sit down \Nand talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.01,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,She's not someone you can just talk to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all this hate business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you hate so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:45.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me why you \Nhate the Clover Kingdom so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:50.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to understand \Neach other when all we ever do is fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.08,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:20.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend also really hated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.10,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The ones you broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.65,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Our golden dreams and our bonds of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.03,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And... he was full of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.83,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Licht, is that person human?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.77,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:16.78,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,There's something strange about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.59,flashback,Wizard King,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that this will become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:22.79,flashback,Wizard King,0000,0000,0000,,a world where our peoples can \Nlive side by side as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.83,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.54,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,Elves' mana is truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.91,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,If we combine that with our techniques \Nin creating magical items,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:35.83,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to make this place \Neven more prosperous and safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.30,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.81,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,We wish you happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.97,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is giving us its blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:01.03,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that our child will be welcomed \Ninto this world with your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.45,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This child is our future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.78,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,the one who'll bring the \Nelves and humans together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.07,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,The humans are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.81,flashback,Elf 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.63,flashback,Elf 3,0000,0000,0000,,My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.51,flashback,Elf 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.86,flashback,Elf 4,0000,0000,0000,,Only that human knows where we live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.61,flashback,Elf 5,0000,0000,0000,,He... He must've betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.14,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:54.56,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.87,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.89,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Who would believe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:33.67,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle all of my hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:36.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a third eye, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That thing just got bigger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did it get bigger, it's using \Nmagic with different attributes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.17,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give us a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.93,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Let the flames of my \Nhatred burn you to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:38.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to bring out my special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.05,main,Akimo,0000,0000,0000,,She's no ordinary mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.56,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.44,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.21,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The wave of hot air was \Nenough to blow me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to get closer to her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:45.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa, Finral, are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:48.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Her insane amount of magic is \Ncreating a mana force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a hard time manipulating space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:13:00.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The second I put my magic\Nthread out, it gets burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That magic power is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:08.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a god incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.70,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.39,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I keep putting out the fires in \Nthe forest, but there's no end to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to extinguish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.33,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is that thing? It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:47.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,L-Looks like I'll have to \Nextinguish the source first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.15,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle uses water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And water can beat fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's evaporating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:07.13,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Spirit Magic: Salamander's Talon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.28,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.13,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.75,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm the one who uses water magic,\Nso I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this... I know I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.71,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this, I can do this, I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.99,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.42,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You've been damaged goods \Never since you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:44.00,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.93,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you managed \Nto pull off the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:50.38,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,at the Water Temple is because \Nyou let your rage take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.34,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You're a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:02.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.86,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:22.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about that flame!\N I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.95,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on! \NYou can do anything if you have the guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's so loud. My ears are ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.76,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me, Noelle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.80,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can figure anything out with guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?! You're a bit too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.16,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Finral! Why are you plugging your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.82,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Feel this wonderful breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:53.75,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, Noelle. \NJust as Asta gave me courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.82,top,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me! \NI'll do it, Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.16,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give Asta courage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.67,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'll probably only be \Nable to use Sea Dragon's Roar once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.18,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,on this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:26.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a failure anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,She dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.26,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.44,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa! That's our Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.66,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:26.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Asta? That's my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:34.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's my comrade! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle's attack managed \Nto subdue the salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.00,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.13,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.57,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now it's finally time \Nfor my special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.81,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:54.57,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mineral Creation Magic: Harpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! How is she able to use \Nmagic besides flame magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's so not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.16,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:12.21,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Phoenix Robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:17.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And she can use recovery magic, too! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And this spell, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.85,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't happen to have a brother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with a really pale face \Nand spiky hair, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's over on the other side \Nof the forest right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.21,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.46,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:01.84,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,If I have any siblings, they're Licht\N and the people of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.37,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Know their grudge against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.22,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll massacre every last one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to her at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to stop her with my \Nspecial move before she recovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:20.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a sec, Asta! What's this \Nspecial move you keep talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.99,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm gonna hold out \Nboth swords in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and charge straight through \Nthe air at super speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.97,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.67,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not without us, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You always come up with the craziest ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let us help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.93,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Remember what I said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:57.14,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are there to help you win \Nagainst a fate you can't defeat on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That attack of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,will end up being incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.65,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.03,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My special move was a complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.73,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.00,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Licht...
