Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.48,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.07,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Over and Over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:49.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Over and Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:54.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:58.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your attacks right \Nback at you over and over and over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:11.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all the narutos you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just eat all the narutos you throw at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:24.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all the natto you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}natto{\i0} gonna let it get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:31.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ew! It's all over my swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to be stabbed by those swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:35.03,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you stupid natto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:38.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Asta! We defeated Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:42.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 60: \N"Defectors' Atonement."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:50.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 60\N\N{\fs18} Defectors' Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:47.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, Charmy. "Atonement" isn't a kind of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:49.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's when you make up for \Nsomething bad you did.
